{"tid":1982411,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港已經淪為偽滿州國、傀儡政權狀態","createTime":"2020-04-21T07:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T08:03:47.000Z","uid":128430,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b407d602488a85d866341f61f44609339311679","tid":1982411,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"滿洲國（1932年3月1日－1945年8月18日）是日本侵佔中國東北後製造之傀儡政權。是在日本的支持下於中國東北地區所成立的獨立於當時中國的政權。<br />\n<br />\n滿洲國的行政機關為國務院，其首長為國務總理。國務院下設總務廳、興安局等機構，並轄有各部門。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總務廳為國務院的政務中樞，由日本人擔任的總務總務長官總攬滿洲國的行政，為實際上的總理。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n總務廳長（總務長官）召集國務院各部的日本裔次官於每週二，即火曜日舉行會議，按關東軍的意志商討並決定國家政策和各種具體事務，被稱為&ldquo;火曜會&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港今日情況一樣，中聯辦才是實際揸莊，香港特首同政府只係傀儡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"4945245ae6fb43acca17845ae54fb72903f51603","tid":1982411,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"58f8cb8bcdea20b2536a650c312ef37cb8198176","tid":1982411,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5f5daf264ae400e7d15c1e472eb0c4ebfa5f9787","tid":1982411,"uid":62799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:56:17.000Z","msg":"丟掉兩制幻想<br />\n正視唯一出路"},{"pid":"86441f826e3cf5b42e1f72064c98aa358679410c","tid":1982411,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d7f1fc681c6c77c35a1d36086fb701688906de4","tid":1982411,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"一直都係，只不過以前係暗裡控制港共"}]}